TextEng: What kind of wares do you sell here?
Can I see your merchandise?
I'd like to ask you some questions.
What you sell? You sell wares?
Me want to buy stuff.
Me have questions.
Goodbye.
Have you heard anything about werewolves near Port Llast?
Text: 라스트 항구 근처에서 늑대인간에 대해 들은 거 있어?

TextEng: I'm looking for work. Do you know of any?
Text: 일거리를 찾고 있어. 혹시 아는 거 있어?

TextEng: I need some directions, actually.
You knows of werewolves, yeah? In Port Llast?
Me needs job. Needs making money. You help?
Text: 나 일 필요해. 돈 벌어야 해. 도와줄래?

TextEng: Me need directions.
Good. Tell me more.
Me likes. Me wants more knowledge, though.
Text: 나 좋아. 근데 나 더 알고 싶어.

TextEng: What are these tomes? What do they do?
Text: 이 비전서들이 뭐야? 뭘 하는 거야?

TextEng: Me not know why you is wanting tomes.
Not interested, but I have another question.
Text: 관심 없어, 근데 다른 질문이 있어.

TextEng: Me not care. Me gots other question.
Text: 나 관심 없어. 나 다른 질문 있어.

TextEng: Yes, I have one.
Me gots reagent. Here you goes.
No, I don't have one.
Me not gots reagent.
What is a reagent?
Me not know. What is reagent?
Actually, can I ask a question instead?
Me rather asks question.
<StartAction>Offer fire beetle's belly reagent.</Start>
<StartAction>Offer bodak's tooth reagent.</Start>
<StartAction>Offer ettercap's silk gland reagent.</Start>
<StartAction>Offer rakshasa's eye reagent.</Start>
<StartAction>Offer slaad's tongue reagent.</Start>
I'd rather not offer a reagent.
Me wanting keep reagent. Me not give.
Text: 나 시약 갖고 싶어. 나 안 줘.

TextEng: Can I ask about something else?
Me gots different question.
What would I have exciting news about?
Me not know what you say. Exciting what?
Text: 나 네가 뭐라는지 몰라. 좋은 뭐?

TextEng: Can you remind me about that job?
Text: 그 일에 대해 다시 말해줄 수 있어?

TextEng: Me needs reminder what me agreed to.
Text: 나 내가 동의한 거 다시 알려줘.

TextEng: I have one of the tomes you seek.
Text: 네가 찾는 비전서 중 하나를 갖고 있어.

TextEng: Me gots tome. You want, still?
Can you remind me about that tome-recovery job?
Text: 그 비전서 회수 일에 대해 다시 말해줄래?

TextEng: Me needs more refreshment 'bout tomes job.
Text: 나 비전서 일에 대해 다시 알려줘.

TextEng: <StartAction>Offer Tome of Fire.</Start>
<StartAction>Offer Tome of Ice.</Start>
<StartAction>Offer Tome of Life.</Start>
<StartAction>Offer Tome of Death.</Start>
<StartAction>Offer Tome of Resonance.</Start>
I have another tome to offer.
Me gots more tome for you.
Text: 나 너한테 줄 비전서 더 있어.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Surely you can provide me with more than that.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 분명 그것보다 더 줄 수 있을 텐데.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me can get more golds, huh?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 금화 더 받을 수 있어, 응?

TextEng: Should I beat more money out of you?
Me can beat more gold from you, yes?
Text: 나 너한테서 금화 더 빼앗아, 응?

TextEng: I'd rather not part with the tomes just yet.
Me thinks me keep tomes for now.
Text: 나 생각에 지금은 비전서 갖고 있을래.

TextEng: Yes, I think that would help.
Text: 응, 그게 도움이 될 것 같아.

TextEng: Me wants refreshment, yes. Tell again, please.
Text: 나 다시 듣고 싶어, 응. 다시 말해줘.

TextEng: Where could the Tome of Fire be?
Do you know where the Tome of Ice is?
I need more information about the Tome of Life.
Text: 생명의 비전서에 대해 더 알아야 해.

TextEng: Help me find the Tome of Death.
Do you know where the Tome of Resonance is?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> I would need a lab.
Me gets Tome of Fire if me knows where is.
Text: 나 어디 있는지 알면 불의 비전서 가져와.

TextEng: Me want to knows where Ice Tome is.
Text: 나 얼음의 비전서 어디 있는지 알고 싶어.

TextEng: Where you thinks Life Tome is?
Where me find Tome of Death?
Where me look for Res'nance Tome?
Who is the Arcane Brotherhood?
What be this brother thingy?
Where is his tomb?
Where me find grave?
Where might I find Saer Bodkin?
Text: 세어 보드킨을 어디서 찾을 수 있을까?

TextEng: Saer Bodkin be where?
<StartAction>Offer skeleton's knuckle reagent.</Start>
<StartAction>Offer fairy dust reagent.</Start>
<StartAction>Offer fenberries reagent.</Start>
<StartAction>Offer quartz crystal reagent.</Start>
